                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <div class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1593530443619-ppa-701---indigenous-public-private-partnerships" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1593530443619-ppa-701---indigenous-public-private-partnerships" aria-controls="accordion-content-1593530443619-ppa-701---indigenous-public-private-partnerships" aria-expanded="false">
                            PPA 701 – Indigenous Public/Private Partnerships
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1593530443619-ppa-701---indigenous-public-private-partnerships" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1593530443619-ppa-701---indigenous-public-private-partnerships">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1593530443619 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="b27fe236-52ce-4eab-93da-3c85ce42f888" >

    <p>This course examines the role of public/private partnerships in the economic development and delivery of services in Aboriginal communities. The challenges and opportunities of First Nations communities partnering with private and public sector organizations will be assessed, particularly in the context of governance and administration issues.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#b27fe236-52ce-4eab-93da-3c85ce42f888");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <div class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1593530443637-ppa-702---administrative-law-in-indigenous-context" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1593530443637-ppa-702---administrative-law-in-indigenous-context" aria-controls="accordion-content-1593530443637-ppa-702---administrative-law-in-indigenous-context" aria-expanded="false">
                            PPA 702 – Administrative Law in Indigenous Context
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1593530443637-ppa-702---administrative-law-in-indigenous-context" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1593530443637-ppa-702---administrative-law-in-indigenous-context">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1593530443637 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="c16d1fab-dabb-4345-a226-2753abf4abb6" >

    <p>This course examines the statutory and regulatory basis of public administration in the context of First Nations communities. It analyzes the regulatory function of administration, as well as the institutional and procedural characteristics and practices of administrative tribunal and judicial review, and assesses their relevance for First Nations communities and peoples.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#c16d1fab-dabb-4345-a226-2753abf4abb6");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <div class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1593530443666-ppa-703---dispute-resolution-in-indigenous-context" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1593530443666-ppa-703---dispute-resolution-in-indigenous-context" aria-controls="accordion-content-1593530443666-ppa-703---dispute-resolution-in-indigenous-context" aria-expanded="false">
                            PPA 703 – Dispute Resolution in Indigenous Context
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1593530443666-ppa-703---dispute-resolution-in-indigenous-context" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1593530443666-ppa-703---dispute-resolution-in-indigenous-context">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1593530443666 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="6e67d4fa-d928-4d5b-afd2-fb9e5b808417" >

    <p>This course introduces students to the field of Alternative Dispute Resolution (ADR), with an in-depth focus on mediation. The course combines basic theory and concepts of ADR and conflict analysis or diagnosis, along with applying ADR in practical situations within Aboriginal communities. Students will assess the relevance of ADR and mediation within an Aboriginal context, and formulate appropriate adaptations.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#6e67d4fa-d928-4d5b-afd2-fb9e5b808417");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <div class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1593530443688-ppa-704---current-issues-in-indigenous-governance" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1593530443688-ppa-704---current-issues-in-indigenous-governance" aria-controls="accordion-content-1593530443688-ppa-704---current-issues-in-indigenous-governance" aria-expanded="false">
                            PPA 704 – Current Issues in Indigenous Governance
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1593530443688-ppa-704---current-issues-in-indigenous-governance" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1593530443688-ppa-704---current-issues-in-indigenous-governance">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1593530443688 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="b0c4489a-482d-4fd1-9d0c-44f6e8c8223d" >

    <p>This course is designed to be responsive to addressing key issues which emerge in the rapidly evolving establishment of Aboriginal governance. Consequently, the issues covered by this course will change from year to year. Possible areas of study include Indian Act reform, Social Policy in the context of Self-Governance, Bill C - 31, Citizenship, the Constitution and Off-Reserve Peoples.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#b0c4489a-482d-4fd1-9d0c-44f6e8c8223d");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <div class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1593530443705-ppa-705---sustainable-development---first-nations" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1593530443705-ppa-705---sustainable-development---first-nations" aria-controls="accordion-content-1593530443705-ppa-705---sustainable-development---first-nations" aria-expanded="false">
                            PPA 705 – Sustainable Development &amp; First Nations
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1593530443705-ppa-705---sustainable-development---first-nations" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1593530443705-ppa-705---sustainable-development---first-nations">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1593530443705 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="f30084c2-50cb-4b70-b2f0-ec6cc57f2dcd" >

    <p>This course will examine alternative models of development for Aboriginal communities. Fundamental concepts of development and progress will be assessed in the context of aboriginal culture and traditions. Examples of alternative and sustainable development in other jurisdictions will be evaluated in terms of their relevance for First Nations communities and nations within Canada.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#f30084c2-50cb-4b70-b2f0-ec6cc57f2dcd");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</div>




